<p>GeoScienceWorld contains a compilation of published materials from various publishers ("Publisher(s)"). The Site allows for searching this material, downloading PDFs with proper access granted, and citation services. </p>
<h2>Permitted Uses</h2>
<p>You have access to the Site and any content that is openly and publicly available or to the Shopping Cart Service that allows for individual purchases of PDFs. You may initiate and complete purchases of local electronic copies using the Site Shopping Cart and have access to content for a limited period of time, provided that such use is subject to all the terms and conditions of this Agreement and does not result in the making available of duplicate copies of the PDFs purchased. You can electronically download and save the PDF purchased for personal use. You can print off PDFs purchased, a single electronic copy for personal use. You will agree to use PDFs purchased consistent with existing "fair use" law and regulation, and that each such copy carries appropriate acknowledgment of the title and author of the material, and its source (publication title, volume, issue, date), publisher, and copyright, and further provided that each electronic copy of such items are deleted when no longer required for such purpose. Nothing in this Agreement in any way excludes, modifies or affects anything you are allowed to do in respect of any of the purchased PDFs consistent with existing "fair use" law, defined by the U.S. Copyright Code of 1976 (17 U.S.C. § 105-107) and international copyright conventions.</p>
<h2>Conditions of Sale</h2>
<p>The Shopping Cart accepts various valid credit card purchases, the cards authorized are subject to change at any time, and validation of the credit card information will be necessary in order to complete a purchase. All purchases available on the Site are in PDF format. Once purchased access to the purchased PDF will be open for a limited period of time to you for you to view and download.</p>
