<p>Any purchase errors should be reported to GeoScienceWorld<a href="https://pubs.geoscienceworld.org/contact-us"> via our contact form</a>.&nbsp;GeoScienceWorld will make every effort to correct the situation. The maximum resolution would involve a refund of the purchase price for PDFs purchased and no more. </p>
