<p>GeoScienceWorld's rights to publish electronically and distribute online the contents of the Site in accordance with this Agreement are granted to GSW by the owners and copyright holders of the publications included in the Site. No provision of this Agreement conveys any ownership interest in or to the Site, in whole or in part, to you. Title, as well as applicable copyrights, patents, trademarks, trade secrets or other intellectual property rights in and to the materials in the Site are, and remain the property of copyright claimants, as applicable.</p>
